\par To build a mecha superstructure from scratch, a character must succeed at a Craft (mechanical) check (DC 30) and a Craft (structural) check (DC 30) after investing the requisite amount of assembly time, based on the mecha\rquote s size: Larg
e 150 hours, Huge 300 hours, Gargantuan 600 hours, Colossal 1,200 hours. A character without a mechanical tool kit takes a \endash 4 penalty on both skill checks. The character must also make a Wealth check against the mecha\rquote s base purchase DC.

