\par }{\b Hardness: }{The amount of damage the material absorbs from a weapon hit or collision.
\par }{\b Base Purchase DC Modifier: }{The modifier applied to the mecha\rquote s base purchase DC.
\par }{\b Restriction: }{Since mecha require a license to own and operate, the materials used for making them do not require special licenses to purchase.
