\par }{\b Base Purchase DC Modifier: }{None.
\par }{\b 
\par NEUTRONITE (PL 7)
\par }{Neutronite is a tough steel alloy into which a weave of free neutrons has been pressed. It is extremely resilient but also incredibly massive, weighing approximately five times more than a similar volume of lead.
\par }{\b Hardness: }{25.
\par }{\b Base Purchase DC Modifier: }{+4.
\par }{\b 
\par MEGATANIUM (PL 8)
\par }{Sandwiched layers of crystal carbon and neovulcanium held in a magnetic matrix, megatanium is exceedingly hard and durable. Megatanium can also be used for armor (see Mecha Armor, below).
\par }{\b Hardness: }{30.
\par }{\b Base Purchase DC Modifier: }{None.
